(15, 'Hot Shapers Fat Blaster Unisex Waist Jacket', 'hot-shapers-fat-blaster-unisex-waist-jacket', '&lt;p&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s Hot Shapers Neotex Slimming Shirt Hot Shapers?&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHot BELT&amp;nbsp;are fitness for everyday wear, with NEOTEX&amp;nbsp;smart fabrics technology that increases core temperature helping your body sweat, sweat, sweat &amp;amp; sweat more while wearing them during daily activities.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHow they work? ?&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe NEOTEX&amp;nbsp;smart fabrics technology in Hot Shapers Neotex Slimming Shirt &amp;nbsp;increases core temperature during your daily activities, at home, exercise, sports, walk, run, baby walk or any physical activity.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHot Shapers clothing can be worn while active regardless of what you are doing&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBenefits:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Maximizes fitness routines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Slim waist tummy and tights&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Increase your core body temperatur&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Improve your overall well-being&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt&amp;rsquo;s all about being in shape.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe more you sweat the fitter you get!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSweat and get in shape.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWashing instructions:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt is recommended to wash it after each use, particularly after exercising.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHand wash in cold water with a soft detergent. Squeeze out and drain.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Hand wash 30&amp;deg;c&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Do not tumble dry &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Do not bleach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Do not iron &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Do not wring &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Do not dry clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;- Line dry / Hang dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '2