(18, 'Micro touch men\'s precision groomer', 'micro-touch-men-s-precision-groomer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Micro Touch &amp;nbsp;easily removes unwanted hair&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGets as close as a blade, yet it&amp;#39;s safe to the touch&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe all in one micro touches personal trimmer&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Micro Touch is a battery-powered personal grooming device that trims hair anywhere with micro precision It&amp;#39;s great for sideburns bushy eyebrows, the back of the neck, mustaches, beards etc.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFeature:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Built-in LED light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Rubber non-slip grip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Trims hair with micro precision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Trim ears, eyebrows, sideburns, back of neck, nostrils, chest anywhere you want to trim/ cut out that extra hair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Get to those hard-to-reach places&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Easy to use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Compact,take it anywhere you want&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Close as a blade yet Safe to the touch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-No pain, irritation or razor bumps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '23', '0', 1600.00, 40, 960.00, 'micro-touch-men-s-precision-groomer-1.jpg,micro-touch-men-s-precision-groomer-2.jpg,micro-touch-men-s-precision-groomer-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(19, 'Riddex Quad Pest Repelling Aid', 'riddex-quad-pest-repelling-aid', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(One unit takes care of a normal sized home, approximately 2000 square feet. Use two units if&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;the house is more than one story).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Extra outlet on the side allows you to use without losing plug space. Includes night light too!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Safe for children and household pets. The Riddex Quad actually changes the normal field&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;around your wiring, creating an environment that aids in the control of pests.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Riddex Quad Repelling Aid is safe for most household pets, except for hamsters, gerbils and&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;other rodent pets. There are no irritating pesticides or fumes. Simply plug this electronic unit&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;into a standard electrical outlet and watch it help drive out pesky pests from your home, in as&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;little as two - three weeks! Designed to work through electrical wiring 230v oulet only.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Electromagnetic Sonic Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Turn Your Home Into A Pest Repellent Force Field&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Electromagnetic, Sonic Repellent, Night Light and Side Outlet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-Non Toxic, No Chemicals, No Poison&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;-For Rodents, Roaches, Ants, Spiders and Other Bugs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Attention: Not suitable for household rodent pets such as gerbil and hamsters&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;1 x Riddex Quad&lt;/p&gt;', '23', '0', 1490.00, 33, 999.00, 'riddex-quad-pest-repelling-aid-1.jpg,riddex-quad-pest-repelling-aid-2.jpg,riddex-quad-pest-repelling-aid-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(20, 'Precise Pedi -  Electric Callus Remover Foot File Waterproof Cordless', 'precise-pedi-electric-callus-remover-foot-file-waterproof-cordless', '&lt;p&gt;Are your feet dry, cracked and covered with callouses? Are you too embarrassed to take your shoes off? Introducing Precise Pedi, the precision beauty device designed to buff away unsightly imperfections and leave your feet and toes smooth, sexy and callous free! With two specially designed Micro Crystal Tips (1 Round Tip and 1 Cone Tip), you&amp;rsquo;ll get precision results quick and easy, even between your toes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Targets and removes callouses and corns. Buffs dry skin for silky smooth results from heel to toe.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Precision roller tips are specially designed for hard to reach areas.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Ergonomic for easy handling.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Motor spins at 3,000 RPM ensuring a smooth finish.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Can be used on dry, cracked and calloused skin on your feet and hands.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Ergonomically designed, comfortable grip.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Lightweight and easy to use.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;BONUS Cone Tip gets between your toes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Requires 2x AA batteries (not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '23', '0', 2650.00, 27, 1935.00, 'precise-pedi-electric-callus-remover-foot-file-waterproof-cordless-1.jpg,precise-pedi-electric-callus-remover-foot-file-waterproof-cordless-2.jpg,precise-pedi-electric-callus-remover-foot-file-waterproof-cordless-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(21, '18 Pcs Handheld Pedi Mate - Gently removes callus, Dry skin', '18-pcs-handheld-pedi-mate-gently-removes-callus-dry-skin', '&lt;p&gt;Handheld Pedi Mate Pedicure Manicure Foot File Nail Shaper Amazing 18 Pieces Tools&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPedi Mate Manicure &amp;amp; Pedicure Set with 2 Handheld Foot Files, Nail Shaper and Attachments &amp;ndash; 18 pieces. The ergonomically designed Pedi Mate is simple and comfortable to use. It has been constructed to gently remove calluses and dead skin and help give your feet an incredibly soft look and feel that you crave. Once you have removed the ugly dead skin, use the emery pads for the finishing. You and your feet will love the Pedi Mate. This set also includes a nail shaper with 10 attachments and a nail shiner so you can groom, buff and shine your nails on your hands and feet for the complete manicure and pedicure. Treat yourself to salon like treatments without the expense with this 18 piece manicure/ pedicure set.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gently removes callous dry skin&lt;br /&gt;\r\n18 piece grooming kit&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUltimate foot file&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNo mess&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSafe to use&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasy to carry&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSpaces for putting each article in its place&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrooms completely&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnique ball tip cone&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBlue stone disc&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBullet cone&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSuperior emery barrel&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProfessional foot cone&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLuxurious buffing barrel&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSatin bristle brush&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFlat disc trimmer&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPrecision pointed cone&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRotary emery board&lt;br /&gt;\r\nComfortable ergonomic design&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBest for feet&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCaptures the fillings&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor smooth sexy feet&lt;/p&gt;', '23', '0', 2750.00, 28, 1980.00, '18-pcs-handheld-pedi-mate-gently-removes-callus-dry-skin-1.jpg,18-pcs-handheld-pedi-mate-gently-removes-callus-dry-skin-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(22, 'Samsung Level Box Pro - Bluetooth Speaker', 'samsung-level-box-pro-bluetooth-speaker', '&lt;p&gt;Samsung LEVEL Box Pro Bluetooth Speaker&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;UHQ(Ultra High Quality) Audio UHQ Audio (96~192kHz/ 24bit) sounds even better than CD quality audio (44.1kHz/ 16bit). UHQ-BT codec technology helps minimise audio loss. Enjoy rich, balanced sound &amp;ndash; almost as good as being in the studio with your favourite musicians&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Powerful Listening ExperienceWith four built-in speakers and two passive radiators, get clear highs, rich mids and deeper bass giving you an incredibly rich, powerful listening experience &amp;ndash; even in larger rooms&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Dual Sound FunctionalityConnect two Level Box Pro units at once for even more power and unbeatable audio richness. Enjoy a more realistic stereo experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Simple Dual-PairingPair your Level Box Pro with up to two devices &amp;ndash; be they smartphones, tablet PCs or laptops. After the first pairing your devices will sync automatically when Bluetooth is enabled.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '32', '0', 5650.00, 30, 3955.00, 'samsung-level-box-pro-bluetooth-speaker-1.jpg,samsung-level-box-pro-bluetooth-speaker-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(23, 'Sensei Slicer - Single Edged Chef\'s Knife', 'sensei-slicer-single-edged-chef-s-knife', '&lt;p&gt;Cuts Paper-Thin Slices&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAir Holes Prevent Sticking&lt;br /&gt;\r\nComfort-Grip Handle&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMirror-Finish Carbon Steel&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDishwasher Safe&lt;br /&gt;\r\n40% Sharper Than Most Chef&amp;#39;s Knives!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDull blades can be dangerous, leading to painful nicks and cuts. But not the Sensei Slicer! Unlike traditional double-beveled blades, its unique 6&amp;quot;L carbon steel blade is only sharpened on one side, which makes it 40% sharper &amp;ndash; and 100% safer!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enjoy Safe, Precision Slicing!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith next-to-no effort you can create paper-thin slices from juicy, ripe tomatoes. And you can use this same, remarkable blade to chop crisp carrots, dice sticky cheese, slice hard, dry salami &amp;ndash; even peel and core tricky, tough pineapples! Japanese-style airholes in the blade prevent food from sticking so one swift, easy motion is all it takes to glide through most every food. The ergonomically designed wooden handle has special gripper dots that increase control while reducing fatigue. Best of all, the Sensei Slicer is dishwasher safe!&lt;/p&gt;', '23', '0', 1590.00, 39, 970.00, 'sensei-slicer-single-edged-chef-s-knife-1.jpg,sensei-slicer-single-edged-chef-s-knife-2.jpg,sensei-slicer-single-edged-chef-s-knife-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(24, 'Smart Swab Easy Earwax Removal', 'smart-swab-easy-earwax-removal', '&lt;p&gt;Smart Swab is a device which allow you to clean your ears by means of a spiral disposable tip.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis product features a handle which looks and feels much like a toothbrush, offering an improved grip over earlier models.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDisposable spiral tips are attached to this handle which allow you to clean your ears more safely than with cotton swabs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHandle. Earlier commercials for Smart Swab show a stick-like handle, but newer images feature a toothbrush-like design. The more recent design offers a superior grip and comfort while using Smart Swab. See images below.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Spiral tip. The key design element of Smart Swab is its soft grooved spiral head which is designed to be twisted in order to collect wax. It is tapered so that it can go into the ear, but not large enough to go too deep. The soft material is not harsh on the delicate inside area of the ear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Disposable? The tips for Smart Swab are meant to be disposable, although there doesn&amp;rsquo;t seem to be any reason why you couldn&amp;rsquo;t disinfect them and re-use. For maximum safety, it is probably a good idea to use a new tip each time, however.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Comfort. Smart Swab is more comfortable to use than a cotton swab because it doesn&amp;rsquo;t reach as deeply into the ear, which is a good thing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;No Batteries Needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Easy Earwax Removal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Soft &amp;amp; Flexible Tip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Prevents Earwax Buildup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Disposable Tips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Includes 1 Smart Swab Handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Includes 16 Tips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '23', '0', 1290.00, 45, 710.00, 'smart-swab-easy-earwax-removal-1.jpg,smart-swab-easy-earwax-removal-2.jpg,smart-swab-easy-earwax-removal-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(25, 'Monster Beats by Dr Dre Mini Bluetooth Speaker', 'monster-beats-by-dr-dre-mini-bluetooth-speaker', '&lt;p&gt;Product Features:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis bluetooth speaker integrated microphone will allow you to keep listening to your music or picking up a phone call .&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(1) Bluetooth Speaker&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(2) Play/pause, Forward/Back, Volume /- buttons&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(3) Integrated microphone&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(4) Handsfree for smartphone&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(5) Li-ion integrated battery&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; Compatible With:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll phones and smartphones with Bluetooth Tecnology :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Apple iPhone 3G 3GS 4 4S 5 5C 5S 6 6Plus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Samsung Galaxy S Advance S2 S3 S4 S5 S6 Egde, Note Note2 Note3 Note4 Tab Core Mega Neo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Sony Xperia&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*LG Optimus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*HTC One&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Google Nexus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Motorola&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Nokia Microsoft Lumia&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Huawei Ascend&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;*Blackberry Mp3 Players with Bluetooth technology.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; Packing List:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;? 1 x Bluetooth Speaker&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;? 1 x Mini USB charging cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;? 1 x User Manual&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '32', '0', 1490.00, 33, 999.00, 'monster-beats-by-dr-dre-mini-bluetooth-speaker-1.jpg,monster-beats-by-dr-dre-mini-bluetooth-speaker-2.jpg,monster-beats-by-dr-dre-mini-bluetooth-speaker-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(26, 'REMAX WK S05 - Adjustable 360 Degree Rotating Car phone Holder', 'remax-wk-s05-adjustable-360-degree-rotating-car-phone-holder', '&lt;p&gt;WK Car Holder Holds The Hand Of Hand-Held Mobile Devices In The Car From The World&amp;#39;s Leading Equipment Manufacturers Smart Phone WK Hong Kong Goods Exported Worldwide. Good Quality Materials For Durability, Robustness, Ease Of Use And Convenience. For Those Who Need A Car. Take The Road For A Long Time Due To The Traffic Jam. Or Have To Travel Far To Use A Hand-Held WK Car Holder Can Be Scaled To Match The Size Of Your Cell.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKey Features&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;middot; Arms Outstretched To Shake Hands Outstretched, Holding A 4.7 To 10 Inches.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;middot; Easy To Install, Requires No Tools.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;middot; Made From Premium Materials More Durable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;middot; 360 Degree Rotation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Package Includes&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1 X WK Remax Mobile Car Holder S05&lt;/p&gt;', '29', '0', 2450.00, 39, 1495.00, 'remax-wk-s05-adjustable-360-degree-rotating-car-phone-holder-1.jpg,remax-wk-s05-adjustable-360-degree-rotating-car-phone-holder-2.jpg,remax-wk-s05-adjustable-360-degree-rotating-car-phone-holder-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(27, 'Dual Purpose Powerful Vacuum Cleaner - Blowing &amp; Sucking', 'dual-purpose-powerful-vacuum-cleaner-blowing-sucking', '&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;inherit&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;1000 W Home &amp;amp; car Vacuum Cleaner Fully Portable for multi purpose use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#111111&quot;&gt;1Portable Vacuum Cleaner (220-240 V, 50 HZ, 1000 W)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#111111&quot;&gt;Lightweight, Handheld Vacuum Cleaner Which Is Ideal For Daily Cleaning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#111111&quot;&gt;It Working Both Suction And Blower Functions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#111111&quot;&gt;Blower Accessory For Multipurpose Use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;backgroun