(28, 'HD Vision Visor - The day &amp; Night Visor for Safer Driving', 'hd-vision-visor-the-day-night-visor-for-safer-driving', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#494848&quot;&gt;HD Vision Visor&amp;#39;s secret is a clear polycarbonate specially tinted to diffuse strong sunlight and glare; and reduce headlight glare at night. It&amp;rsquo;s simple, easy, and requires no special tools or batteries. It works on any car, truck, or caravan as long as you have a visor already installed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;inherit&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#494848&quot;&gt;Reduces blinding glare from the sun during the day&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;inherit&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#494848&quot;&gt;Brightens vision and cuts harsh headlight glare at night&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;inherit&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#494848&quot;&gt;Enhances colour, clarity and contrast&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot