(37, 'Programmable  Electric Pressure Cooker', 'programmable-electric-pressure-cooker', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The multi-cooker replaces 7 common kitchen appliances&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;pressure cooker, slow cooker, rice cooker, saut&amp;eacute;, steamer, warmer, makes cake. Help you cook delicious, flavorful and healthier meals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;The pressure cooker include 15&amp;nbsp;Smart Built-In Programs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Elite/Quick cooking (rice), Congee, Beef, Soup, Chicken, Meat, Fish, Cake, Enyrecote, Baby Food, Stew, Preset and Keep Warm/Cancel.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Fast and Safe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Compared with other traditional cookers, this pressure cooker preserves natural flavors, nutrients and vitamins with up to 70?ster performance. It conforms to CE, ROHS, and EMC, ensuring safety for daily use by beginners or professionals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Versatile electric pressure cooker for personal requirements&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;14 Built-in smart cooking programs for different cooking methods&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;6Qt capacity/1000W 220V&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Convenient Preset function can delay your cooking time for up to 24 hours&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Removable non-stick inner pot for easy cooking and cleaning&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Reinforced stainless steel exterior for scratch resistance&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Detachable seal ring and lid for proper and effortless cleaning&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Saving energy, money and time&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull;Kitchen and environment friendly&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warm Tips&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1.To avoid hot steam, do Not pull out the exhaust valve by hand when the pressure cooker just finished working.&lt;