(44, '2 in 1 Hair Straightening &amp;amp; Curling Iron - GM 2961', '2-in-1-hair-straightening-curling-iron-gm-2961', '&lt;p&gt;Straightener 2 in 1 Gemei Model: 2961. Straightener with aluminum plates with ceramic coating 50W. Effectively straightens out and twisting hair strands. A good choice for people who want a smooth haircut that does not need to be constantly improved. Thanks to ceramic coating, hair is much less damaged than metal straighteners. The lightener is lightweight and comfortable to use. It has a rotating cable that does not wobble when preparing a hairstyle. The straightener can be used to spin hair, which increases its functionality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Ideal for straightening and curling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Fast heating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Aluminum plates with ceramic coating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;360 degree rotating cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Power: 30W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '27', '0', 3750.00, 34, 2475.00, '2-in-1-hair-straightening-curling-iron-gm-2961-1.jpg,2-in-1-hair-straightening-curling-iron-gm-2961-2.jpg,2-in-1-hair-straightening-curling-iron-gm-2961-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(45, 'Rechargeable Callus Remover - Foot Care', 'rechargeable-callus-remover-foot-care', '&lt;p&gt;Callus can be really annoying and painful. It can also make your feet look very unappealing.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThat&amp;#39;s why you need this callus remover. This will help remove callus from your feet so you have no embarrassment about them anymore.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFeatures:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Simple design.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;It leaves skin smooth and polish.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Push-type switch, easy to operation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Painless technology to remove dead skin.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Unique rollers grindingSafer &amp;amp; more efficient, easy &amp;amp; fun to use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Contains one more Quality, Durable, Coarse Roller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Rechargable Economic &amp;amp; Green Environmental Protection&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Water Proof design Wet &amp;amp; Dry use, easy for clean and more comfortable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '27', '0', 3390.00, 27, 2475.00, 'rechargeable-callus-remover-foot-care-1.jpg,rechargeable-callus-remover-foot-care-2.jpg,rechargeable-callus-remover-foot-care-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(46, 'Rechargeable Nose &amp; Hair Trimmer', 'rechargeable-nose-hair-trimmer', '&lt;p&gt;The procedure of hair removal is painless and takes only a few minutes;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSafe cutting system&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSafe cutting unit&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDry use&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCurved stainless steel blades&lt;br /&gt;\r\nErgonomic design, compact size is easy to take with you&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPowered by Built-in Battery&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCharging from the network&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasy to clean with a brush (included)&lt;/p&gt;', '27', '0', 2556.00, 30, 1790.00, 'rechargeable-nose-hair-trimmer-1.jpg,rechargeable-nose-hair-trimmer-2.jpg,rechargeable-nose-hair-trimmer-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(47, 'Stallion Cordless Hair Trimmer', 'stallion-cordless-hair-trimmer', '&lt;p&gt;The Stallion Cordless Rechargeable Beard and Mustache Trimmer offers a durable housing and precision-ground steel blades for consistent, precise trimming. Made from Titanium Plated self-sharpening blades stay sharp for a long time. Plus, you can operate the Stallion Rechargeable Beard and Mustache Trimmer with or without a cord. It can be powered by the rechargeable battery or plugged into an outlet with its charger for direct power.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Streamline Modelling / best ergonomic design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Advanced shaving system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Powerful motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;High capacity rechargeable batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Mute design / noise lower than similar products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Light &amp;amp; compact&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Streamlined model / Best ergonomic design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Titanium plated steel cutting blades&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Whisper-Quiet operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Low vibration design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Non-Slip hand grip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '27', '0', 2271.00, 30, 1590.00, 'stallion-cordless-hair-trimmer-1.jpg,stallion-cordless-hair-trimmer-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(48, '7 In 1 One Touch Kitchen Can Opener Can Do', '7-in-1-one-touch-kitchen-can-opener-can-do', '&lt;p&gt;7 in 1 Kitchen Cando Can Opener&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A wonderful kitchen must have tool for preparation of food in can or bottle.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFlip up the swivel handle to open cans. Use the jaws to break vacuum seals, the gripper to twist off caps and the notch to pop off bottle caps, and more you can think of with this Kitchen Can-Do multipurpose tool. Maximizes results by offering you instant access to virtually any vessel. Open cans without leaving sharp edges, pry tins, lift tabs, break seals, twist caps and much more.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKitchen Can Do : its a must in kitchen and when in travel , camping, hiking , fishing and Trekking.&lt;/p&gt;', '23', '0', 1295.00, 39, 790.00, '7-in-1-one-touch-kitchen-can-opener-can-do-1.jpg,7-in-1-one-touch-kitchen-can-opener-can-do-2.jpg,7-in-1-one-touch-kitchen-can-opener-can-do-3.jpg', 1, 1),
