(53, 'Portable Car Vacuum Cleaner', 'portable-car-vacuum-cleaner', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Vaccum Cleaner Portable.Powerful and Reliable Car Vacuum Cleaner Need not wait for that once in a while dry-cleaning sessions for your car. Now feel confident in letting your friends or colleagues be seated anywhere in your car without caring that they will find the crumbs of the potato chips or snacks that you had enjoyed yesterday evening in your car. Even if you hire a person to clean your car daily, or even if you do it yourself, a few untidy nuisances always escape your sight and stay there in the deep, dark interiors of your car. Keep your car regularly clean with this amazing and powerful vacuum cleaner with the long handle attachment that reaches the most difficult corner areas in your car. Features: 12V power Just plug-n-play using the cigarette lighter power socket&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feature:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Powerful suction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Compact and lightweight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Used directly from the car lighter socket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Complete with convenient attachment and washable filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Controlled by ON / OFF switch, easy to use.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Suit for travel and all vehicles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '29', '0', 3461.00, 35, 2250.00, 'portable-car-vacuum-cleaner-1.jpg,portable-car-vacuum-cleaner-2.jpg', 1, 1),
