(55, 'Facial Hydrate Steamer Mist and Sauna Inhaler', 'facial-hydrate-steamer-mist-and-sauna-inhaler', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facial Hydrate Steamer Mist and Sauna Inhaler Home Spa Face Skin Care&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can treat yourself to luxurious spa treatments in the comfort of your own home with this Facial Sauna System. Simply activate the hydrophilic factor and replenish water in your skin. This facial steamer promotes the regeneration of collagen, reduces hairline cracks and wrinkles and helps to restore your skin for a soft, smoother complexion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;your skin will be sparkling clean and fresh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Masal mask and facial steamer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Air-hole for breathing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Easy to switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Constant-temperature heating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Rapid fog-emitting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Face cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Moisturizing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Sauna&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Fits men &amp;amp; women&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '27', '0', 3986.00, 25, 2990.00, 'facial-hydrate-steamer-mist-and-sauna-inhaler-1.jpg,facial-hydrate-steamer-mist-and-sauna-inhaler-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(56, 'JBL Everest 100 In-Ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphone', 'jbl-everest-100-in-ear-wireless-bluetooth-headphone', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;BL Everest Elite 100 is legendary sound in an on-the-go design. Bluetooth 4.1 technology enables wireless connectivity, JBL Pro Audio Sound delivers a dynamic listening experience, and ergonomic earpieces allow for unprecedented fit, and comfort in your ears. A rechargeable battery offers 8 hours of performance, and its built in microphone with echo cancellation technology provides more natural sounding voice calls. Enjoy ultimate sound &amp;amp;ndash; unbo&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '32', '0', 2945.00, 44, 1650.00, 'jbl-everest-100-in-ear-wireless-bluetooth-headphone-1.jpg,jbl-everest-100-in-ear-wireless-bluetooth-headphone-2.jpg,jbl-everest-100-in-ear-wireless-bluetooth-headphone-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(57, 'Spin scrubber - The ‘reach anywhere’ cordless power scrubber', 'spin-scrubber-the-reach-anywhere-cordless-power-scrubber', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The amazing Hurricane Spin Scrubber&lt;/strong&gt; does the hard work so you don&amp;#39;t have to. Its powerful, flexible bristles cut through tough dirt, mildew and soap scum without harsh chemicals. With 300 scrubs per minute, your cleaning time is cut in half. It&amp;#39;s cordless, so you can clean without fumbling over wires or searching for outlets. A single charge lasts up to 60 minutes. For indoor/outdoor use. 5-7/8&amp;quot;W x 6-3/8&amp;quot;D x 21-3/8&amp;quot;H. Plastic, polyurethane and aluminum.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The easy way to scrub! No bending, no hard work!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDoes the hard work for you!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHelpful to those with arthritis or limited dexterity&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Works on:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTile, Grout, Showers,Tubs, Sinks,&amp;nbsp;Door tracks, Patio furniture, Wheels, Boats, Bicycles, &amp;amp; more!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Powerful 300 RPM cleaning action&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Includes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Hurricane Spin Scrubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;3 Scrubbing heads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Multipurpose brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Corner brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Extra-wide flat brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Extension pole&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;AC adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '23', '0', 6370.00, 38, 3950.00, 'spin-scrubber-the-reach-anywhere-cordless-power-scrubber-1.jpg,spin-scrubber-the-reach-anywhere-cordless-power-scrubber-2.jpg,spin-scrubber-the-reach-anywhere-cordless-power-scrubber-3.jpg', 1, 1),
(58, 'Stylish Shoe rack', 'stylish-shoe-rack', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portable 5 Tier Shoe Rack Shelf - Holds upto 15 Pairs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaterial: Stainless Steel and Hard Plastic&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the Huayida 5 Tier Shoe Rack your collection can be displayed neatly within the bedroom or wardrobe. Holding up to 15 pairs of shoes, this shoe rack should be enough for most style icons; you may even have some free space left for your partner&amp;#39;s or children&amp;#39;s shoes&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Light weight &amp;amp; Portable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Hard Plastic with Metal Rod&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Easy to Fold &amp;amp; Store&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Become a Smart Home Maker and Organize Your Shoes in this Shoe Rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Height: 26 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Width: 22 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Depth: 6 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '25', '6', 2355.00, 30, 1649.00, 'stylish-shoe-rack-1.jpg,stylish-shoe-rack-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(59, 'Glass Water Bottle - The Right Amount of Water Every Day!', 'glass-water-bottle-the-right-amount-of-water-every-day', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt; Drink the right amount of water every day!&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt; Made of 100% recycled glass with a 750 ml capacity, this bottle indicates excatly the right amount of water intake to keep you hydrated through out the day..&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '27', '0', 1499.00, 38, 930.00, 'glass-water-bottle-the-right-amount-of-water-every-day-1.jpg,glass-water-bottle-the-right-amount-of-water-every-day-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(60, '40 Pcs Wrench Tool Set', '40-pcs-wrench-tool-set', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fix Every Thing With AIWA 40 PCS. TOOL SET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCrafted from metal, this Aiwa Wrench Set contains 35 sockets of different sizes and shapes, so you can definitely find a correct match, whatever the repair you need to work on. These sockets and wrenches can work on metric fasteners to reduce slippage for greater safety and make it impossible to damage them. Whether you need some fixing on your car, bike, or home appliances, you can easily carry this easy-to-use socket wrench set thanks to its sturdy case.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AIWA Wrench Set&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 3/8&amp;quot; Reversible Ratchet Handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 3/8&amp;quot; DR. x 3&amp;quot; Extension Bar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 1/4&amp;quot; (M) x 3/8&amp;quot; (F) Adaptor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 1/4&amp;quot; DR. x 6&amp;quot; Spinner Handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 3/8&amp;quot; DR. 5/8&amp;quot; Spark Plug Socket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x Storage Blow Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 1/4&amp;quot; DR. 8PT. Socket 1/4&amp;quot; 5/16&amp;quot; 3/8&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 1/4&amp;quot; DR. 5/32&amp;quot; 3/16&amp;quot; 7/32&amp;quot; 1/4&amp;quot; 9/32&amp;quot; 5/16&amp;quot; 11/32&amp;quot; 3/8&amp;quot; 13/32&amp;quot; 7/16&amp;quot; 15/32-1/2&amp;quot; 17/32&amp;quot; 9/16&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;14 x 1/4&amp;quot; DR. 4 4.5 5 5.5 6 6.5 7 7.5 8 9 10 11 12 13 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1 x 3/8&amp;quot; Dr.x21mm Spark Plug Socket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;2 x 3/8&amp;quot; DR Socket: 15mm 16mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;1/4&amp;quot; &amp;amp; 3/8&amp;quot; Drive S.A.E&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '29', '0', 2125.00, 40, 1275.00, '40-pcs-wrench-tool-set-1.jpg,40-pcs-wrench-tool-set-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(61, 'Hand Operated Manual Juicer', 'hand-operated-manual-juicer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This juicer&lt;/strong&gt; can be utilized to prepare fruit as well as vegetable juices for cooking and drinking purposes. It is made of fine quality abs plastic that will last you a long period of time and will also be convenient to use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The juicer comes with detachable parts and also has a glass that will collect the juice. It is equipped with a waste bin which will collect unwanted pulp.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Material: Plastic Stainless steel&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It can be used for both indoor and outdoor purposes&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExtremely sharp and hardened stainless steel blade&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Color: Green&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '24', '4', 2500.00, 42, 1450.00, 'hand-operated-manual-juicer-1.jpg,hand-operated-manual-juicer-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(62, 'IGIA Vibro Shape - Professional Slimming Unit', 'igia-vibro-shape-professional-slimming-unit', '&lt;p&gt;Vibro Shape is a &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;professional vibrating belt&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt; that helps tone muscles in areas such as the abdominals, buttocks, thighs, shoulders and calves. This fitness belt breaks down fat cells, improves blood circulation and increases muscle strength. The Vibro Shape fits waists ranging from 24 to 55 inches. It has five low-power and five high-power setting options. Put simply, this belt provides high-frequency massage vibrations. It comes with a remote that is attached to the belt. Furthermore, this fitness device mimics chiropractic treatments, relieve stress and promote good digestion. You simply strap on the Vibro Shape and use it for 10 minutes each day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Assists slimming, digestion and relaxation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Variable settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Heat diffusion to ease blood circulation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;5 level auto and manual control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Controls for programme, speed and direction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li&gt;Power: 220V-240V/ 50Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '23', '0', 7350.00, 33, 4925.00, 'igia-vibro-shape-professional-slimming-unit-1.jpg,igia-vibro-shape-professional-slimming-unit-2.jpg', 1, 1),
(63, 'Twin Kit (Standard) - E-Cigarette  E-Shisha Pen Kit', 'twin-kit-standard-e-cigarette-e-shisha-pen-kit', '&lt;p&gt;Twin Standard Starter Kit with Atomizer, Battery &amp;amp; USB Charger&lt;br /&gt;\r\neGo Standard Battery&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWickless Atomizer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCE &amp;amp; RoHS Approved&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFree Leather Zipper Case&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFree 2 liquid Refill Juice Flavours Oil&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This eGo CE5 Twin Standard Starter Kit is a great way to begin your vaping experience and join the many e-cig users. This kit is built with the highest quality materials to ensure you get a smooth and tasteful vape. The kit comes with a CE5 Wickless Rebuildable Atomizer, Original eGO-T Battery , two liquid Refill flovor oils &amp;amp; USB Charger.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAtomizer/Clearomizer - The CE5 is wickless and made from the highest quality materials. This means you will get no burning taste or leaking from your e-cig. The atomizer holds 1.6ml of e-liquid and is completely rebuildable and washable so you can change between flavours without any hassle. Available in 7 colours.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBattery - Original eGO battery available, Charging time is approximately 3-4 hours and normal working voltage is 3.7-4.2 volts. The battery is compatible with all 510 thread and eGo style atomizers and come in a range of different battery capacities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Cleaning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWash the Atomizer only in warm water. The best way to clean the wicks is to fill the unit half way with warm water, put the top on and then shake vigorously. This method should be repeated 3-4 times until the colour of the wick is as close to white as possible. Leave to dry and re-use.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;How to use&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo fill the CE5 Atomizer, simply unscrew the mouth tip and pour the liquid along the side of the tank avoiding getting liquid into the centre hole. Fill up to the line where it says 1.6ml. Screw the mouth tip back on and connect it to the battery. Leave to stand for 10 minutes and then begin to vape. To switch the battery on/off just press the on/off battery 5 times repeatedly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contents&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2x CE5 Atomizer&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2x eGo Standard Battery&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1x USB Charger (wall plug not included)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1x Leather Zipper Case&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2x liquid Refill Juice Flavours Oil&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '32', '0', 3750.00, 34, 2475.00, 'twin-kit-standard-e-cigarette-e-shisha-pen-kit-1.jpg,twin-kit-standard-e-cigarette-e-shisha-pen-kit-2.jpg,twin-kit-standard-e-cigarette-e-shisha-pen-kit-3.jpg', 1, 1);

